# OpenAI API Configuration

# Option 1: Single API Key (Default)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-key-here

# Option 2: Multiple API Keys (Load Balancing - NO RATE LIMITS!)
# Uncomment and add multiple keys separated by commas
# OPENAI_API_KEYS=sk-proj-key1,sk-proj-key2,sk-proj-key3,sk-proj-key4,sk-proj-key5

# How to get multiple keys:
# 1. Create multiple OpenAI accounts (or use team members' keys)
# 2. Each account gets its own rate limit
# 3. System automatically rotates between keys
# 4. Effectively UNLIMITED requests!

# Example with 5 keys (5x rate limit):
# OPENAI_API_KEYS=sk-proj-abc123...,sk-proj-def456...,sk-proj-ghi789...,sk-proj-jkl012...,sk-proj-mno345...
